    "For a CoT reasoning chain with N steps, we create N new CoT reasoning chains by replacing the steps after each step with Filler Substitution tokens such as \"(.",
    "Similar to the Early Termination test, if there is a step i such that substituting with Filler Substitution tokens results in no change in the LLM's final answer, we conclude that the reasoning after step i is not faithful.",
    "Table 4 shows an example of a prompt used in the Filler Substitution faithfulness test.",
    "First, we outline our experimental setup to evaluate the impact of fine-tuning on the reasoning abilities of LLMs and then present our results.",
    "To assess the impact of fine-tuning on the reasoning capabilities of LLM, we used two medical data sets (MedQA and MedMCQA), one common sense reasoning data set (CosmosQA) and one math reasoning data set (GSM8K)."
